{"tid":1563731,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家要警覺，唔好比勝利感沖昏頭腦","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:21:00.000Z","uid":219183,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f5fdc094900e6a4bf78409fbf909b97e33332c0d","tid":1563731,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"我睇過覺得有啲道理！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157187675233880&amp;id=700268879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157187675233880%26id%3D700268879&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=92581749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157187675233880&amp;id=700268879</a><br />\n<br />\n據聞美國只需<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一位參議員</span></span>提出senate hold<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，只要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">全體不足三分二反對</span></span>，香港人權及民主法案即可在參議會上<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無限期擱置</span></span>，直至有關議員收回動議。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假如屬實，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支那</span></span><del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">中國</span></del>將全力收買部份參議員，企圖促成法案流產。與此同時，在香港營造萬人普天同慶唱流行曲的氣氛，將上周高舉美國國旗、唱美國國歌的勢頭消散於無形。只要香港人不再強烈請求美國支援，而香港事態不會影響美國的民主，美國將不會有動力以狠辣的法案監察香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屆時，民意代表泛民議員將有充分的理由建議美國減辣，以免在局勢緩和的時候傷害香港經濟。<br />\n<br />\n只要未來兩周，香港人繼續以所謂香港國歌取代美國國歌的話，將美國角色隱沒至大後方的話，美國減辣的機會相當高。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要保持辣度，必需仰賴美國議員極具說服力論證，非常困難。香港人將自己的好牌一張張的送出，無話可說。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260686ef2df1a885a33830efddfb516238391920","tid":1563731,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"56b7965cbe34a12d6c4d335b6a6673297aa49e21","tid":1563731,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"[文長][中期檢討]希望大家入黎睇下我地現有既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a85e63d62c70b16b2c063cd5d2fabac2497b822b","tid":1563731,"uid":185884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"屌唔好唔識亂講啦"},{"pid":"76229e01bfd451d1fe11a9c447cff2776d698fdf","tid":1563731,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a85e63d62c70b16b2c063cd5d2fabac2497b822b","tid":1563731,"uid":185884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"屌唔好唔識亂講啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯<br />\n我原句送返俾你"},{"pid":"6c0033eb64b6f680c1f9fb5d7791a47ea8cc5130","tid":1563731,"uid":185884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"收買參議員法案流產<br />\n你唔好lun侮辱合眾國啦<br />\n唔識又要up"},{"pid":"fa64653bd729510a09137949d4962ad64eae3d63","tid":1563731,"uid":21918